### Test Vocabulary API Endpoints
### Sử dụng với REST Client extension trong VS Code

### 1. Tạo Vocabulary Topic
POST http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-topics
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicName": "Family & Relationships",
  "description": "Từ vựng về gia đình và các mối quan hệ",
  "image": "https://example.com/family.jpg",
  "orderIndex": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

### 2. Lấy danh sách Vocabulary Topics
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-topics

### 3. Lấy chi tiết Vocabulary Topic
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-topics/1

### 4. Lấy thống kê Vocabulary Topic
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-topics/1/stats

### 5. Tạo Vocabulary
POST http://localhost:8001/vocabularies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topicId": 1,
  "englishWord": "family",
  "pronunciation": "/ˈfæməli/",
  "vietnameseMeaning": "gia đình",
  "wordType": "Noun",
  "difficultyLevel": "Easy",
  "image": "https://example.com/family.jpg",
  "audioFile": "https://example.com/family.mp3",
  "isActive": true
}

### 6. Lấy danh sách Vocabularies
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabularies

### 7. Lấy Vocabularies theo topic
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabularies?topicId=1

### 9. Lấy Vocabularies theo topic ID
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabularies/topic/1

### 10. Lấy chi tiết Vocabulary
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabularies/1

### 11. Tạo Vocabulary Example
POST http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-examples
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vocabularyId": 1,
  "englishSentence": "My family is very important to me.",
  "vietnameseSentence": "Gia đình tôi rất quan trọng với tôi.",
  "audioFile": "https://example.com/family-example.mp3"
}

### 12. Lấy danh sách Vocabulary Examples
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-examples

### 13. Lấy Examples theo vocabulary
GET http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-examples/vocabulary/1

### 14. Tạo User Vocabulary Progress
POST http://localhost:8001/user-vocabularies-progress
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "vocabularyId": 1,
  "status": "Learning",
  "masteryLevel": 0,
  "timesPracticed": 0
}

### 15. Lấy danh sách User Vocabulary Progress
GET http://localhost:8001/user-vocabularies-progress

### 16. Lấy Progress theo user
GET http://localhost:8001/user-vocabularies-progress/user/1

### 17. Lấy thống kê user
GET http://localhost:8001/user-vocabularies-progress/user/1/stats

### 18. Cập nhật Progress sau luyện tập (trả lời đúng)
POST http://localhost:8001/user-vocabularies-progress/practice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "vocabularyId": 1,
  "practiceResult": true
}

### 19. Cập nhật Progress sau luyện tập (trả lời sai)
POST http://localhost:8001/user-vocabularies-progress/practice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "vocabularyId": 1,
  "practiceResult": false
}

### 20. Cập nhật Vocabulary Topic
PATCH http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-topics/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Từ vựng về gia đình và các mối quan hệ - Cập nhật"
}

### 21. Cập nhật Vocabulary
PATCH http://localhost:8001/vocabularies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "difficultyLevel": "Medium"
}

### 22. Cập nhật Vocabulary Example
PATCH http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-examples/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "englishSentence": "My family means everything to me."
}

### 23. Cập nhật User Vocabulary Progress
PATCH http://localhost:8001/user-vocabularies-progress/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "masteryLevel": 85,
  "status": "Mastered"
}

### 24. Xóa Vocabulary Example
DELETE http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-examples/1

### 25. Xóa User Vocabulary Progress
DELETE http://localhost:8001/user-vocabularies-progress/1

### 26. Xóa Vocabulary
DELETE http://localhost:8001/vocabularies/1

### 27. Xóa Vocabulary Topic
DELETE http://localhost:8001/vocabulary-topics/1
